OCAX(x)

This software is BETA.
We have frozen new features and are ironing out bugs.
Recommended install is via GIT so you can update easily.
Please get in touch.


Directory structure
|
- app
|
- protected
|
- framework	(http://www.yiiframework.com/ (version 1.1.13))


Installation

Create database
CREATE DATABASE db_name CHARACTER SET latin1 COLLATE latin1_swedish_ci;
and tables
mysql -uuser_name -p db_name < schema.sql

Copy protected/config/main.example.php to protected/config/main.php
Modify mysql connection parameters in protected/config/main.php

File permissions
chown -R www-data protected/runtime/ protected/data/
chown www-data app/assets/

apt-get install zip

